1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes mandatory standards for all service-related operational communications conducted by Elko County Information Operations (ECIO) Department personnel with end users,
 internal stakeholders,
 vendors,
 and external partners.
\end_layout

