noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 (Operational Incident Management Policy) and the communication standards of this policy remain in effect unless a Chapter 4 incident is declared.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Operational Outage Notifications
\series default
:
 The IT Director and designated Information Operations Personnel shall follow the stakeholder notification standards defined in 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
